title: Blacks On Blondes - Iris Rose
description:
Iris Rose loves older men. She doesn't really care how much older...just so they're older than her. Iris says, "boys my age are immature and stupid!" Enter Mandingo. He's friends with Iris's dad, and he's here ready to play a round of gold with her old man. What Mandingo doesn't know is he had an emergency at work come up, and it was so sudden and severe no one got a hold of Mandingo to tell him the golf day is off. Iris has had her eyes on Mandingo ever since her dad and "Dingo" became friends, and now that she's 18, Iris is going to make her move. And what a move it is.
